mods.abstract: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Tate Moore performing songs from his album "Old Dead Dog" with Chris Ethridge of the Flying Burrito Bros., Jeff Colburn of the Kudzu Kings, and David Gilmore of the Circuit Riders at Proud Larry's on December 7 and George Street Grocery on December 8.
